<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV114">
<l>īṉamāya veṭṭunīkki yētamiṉṟi mītupōy</l>
<l>vāṉamāḷa vallaiyēlva ṇaṅkivāḻtteṉ neñcamē</l>
<l>ñāṉamāki ñāyiṟāki ñālamuṟṟu mōreyiṟ</l>
<l>ṟēṉamāyi ṭantamūrtti yentaipāta meṇṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart! Worship and praise [Him] if you are capable of ruling over Heaven</l>
<l>Going above without suffering, having removed all eight inferior [issues],</l>
<l>Thinking of the feet of my Father, the Lord who, as a one-tusked boar, scooped out</l>
<l>The whole world, being knowledge, being the sun.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
